description:
Aide and maid to Aliceliese. An astral elementaler of Earth, and an expert fighter who is skilled in all martial arts. Very good at assassination techniques as well, and can assess any situation accurately. She is committed to Aliceliese whom she idolizes, but has a hard time coping with Aliceliese`s whimsical behaviors, too.
Source: Official page
name: Rin Vispose
